# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Brand Ad Generator — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in your keys.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────


# ── REQUIRED ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Gemini API Key (Google AI Studio)
# Get yours free at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSyD7MsWnIELH2Grnr9ieckyZTw-JKjICADU


# ── OPTIONAL (tool works without these; VoC sources are skipped gracefully) ───

# Reddit API — needed for Reddit consumer discussions
# How to get (free, ~2 min):
#   1. Go to https://www.reddit.com/prefs/apps
#   2. Click "Create another app..." at the bottom
#   3. Choose "script", give it any name (e.g. "brand-ad-gen")
#   4. Set redirect URI to: http://localhost:8080
#   5. Copy the client ID (under the app name) and the secret
REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=your_reddit_client_id_here
REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=your_reddit_client_secret_here

# YouTube Data API v3 — needed for YouTube review comment scraping
# How to get (free, 10 000 units/day, ~5 min):
#   1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
#   2. Create a new project (or use an existing one)
#   3. Go to APIs & Services → Library
#   4. Search "YouTube Data API v3" → Enable
#   5. Go to APIs & Services → Credentials → Create Credentials → API key
#   6. Copy the key below (no billing required for the free quota)
YOUTUBE_API_KEY=your_youtube_api_key_here
